CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1962, pg. 14A, reads: " Holiday House Glistens With D.I.'s Style Show and Dance Benefit for MENDS, the National Foundation for Neuromuscular Diseases, Inc."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing light colored sleeveless embroidered floral dress with matching hat, jeweled circular pendant, and light colored gloves, standing in front of musicians in the Holiday House for D.I. Club's "Melody in Fashions" benefit for MENDS
